{"tid":297592,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打有脊柱側彎喱個病?","createTime":"2017-06-25T15:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T14:25:50.000Z","uid":102978,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81faf29bc1a9874fa35e0f4fe9d22483cc1d0de2","tid":297592,"uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打都比喱個症困擾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n據我所知有得做手術改善但個手術會影響一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔做手術有冇其他方法可以改善?<br />\n巴打們又有冇睇過脊醫係真係醫到個病?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e7a328cd017c3cb6f189fc99938615a1771503","tid":297592,"uid":33567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:40:12.000Z","msg":"少過二十度又唔痛 基本上改善下姿勢 平時做下運動平衡返背肌 不出半年就有明顯好轉"},{"pid":"bcd983cdc34c309f8a8829ed4edc9e56da4f8ee5","tid":297592,"uid":46633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:41:33.000Z","msg":"成日腰酸背痛，但係唔想做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fc8452ae89dcfa37553b314ebac6c337f8f183","tid":297592,"uid":121972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"以前有依個症，之後去症針灸三個月左右，就好番<br />\n<br />\n利申：非嚴重，睇西醫個時話彎左幾度，之後開始針灸"},{"pid":"911d83c16116da924b54a6c8dabfecab25efad1a","tid":297592,"uid":46633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前有依個症，之後去症針灸三個月左右，就好番<br />\n<br />\n利申：非嚴重，睇西醫個時話彎左幾度，之後開始針灸</blockquote><br />\nDetails <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇左幾錢同痛唔痛？"},{"pid":"f0e4dbbd5eb3285e0dcf7670f29658c81b102ccf","tid":297592,"uid":61306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"21度 留名"},{"pid":"75c0620e839e46b8dabd695bc56741e7370bbc53","tid":297592,"uid":