img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打最好去搵間醫院照個x-ray睇下<br />\n因為通常冇效嘅治療先會由single curve變到double curve<br />\n好似你咁本身得lower back有事，但依家變到頸椎都有埋事其實幾大獲，好大機會係你個脊椎為左compensate lower back嘅curve 而 induce左 頸椎嘅 curve，換句話姐係你依家嘅治療唔夠/冇效<br />\n如果繼續係咁只會越黎越彎"},{"pid":"af19baa3f38c30de1052fc0e3853c0d0f5726573","tid":297592,"uid":48021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"22歲 20度<br />\n除左腰骨痛都無乜問題"},{"pid":"355a462743b19adf66efd383e7405db6d6c046b1","tid":297592,"uid":65386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:41:25.000Z","msg":"19歲38度 佢話40度要帶架或者做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fce6b0009c07351a63f20886a12cafed535a06","tid":297592,"uid":126199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"我係天生就有類似脊柱側彎呢個病，如果你係後天嘅話姐係好大機會係遺傳（我教授講嘅）但好似你咁嘅情況嘅話你要定期check特別係如果你依家係青春期，因為青春期影響你嘅度數特別大。如果未係好嚴重就可以問一下醫生意見洗吾洗整腰箍，而且要游多啲水，盡量保持你腰嘅flexibility 同加一個陸上運動to keep your bone strong 。如果你係女仔嘅話更要留意，因為25歲係骨嘅癲瘋期之後只會跌不會升。最後，你最好都係好睇醫生因爲可以突然歪得好緊要，如果要睇最好睇中大同港大嘅 因為佢地專負研究呢方面"},{"pid":"d644ce1dc55ed32a3a865bc8ecaf3e73bd33b76e","tid":297592,"uid":41960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"想幫朋友問，如果一個女人有30度左右側彎，去到30歲後係咪好易惡化？"},{"pid":"c5e669c017f1131b5746ad1a88250a74a0a48383","tid":297592,"uid":86856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打都比喱個症困擾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n據我所知有得做手術改善但個手術會影響一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔做手術有冇其他方法可以改善?<br />\n巴打們又有冇睇過脊醫係真係醫到個病?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打幾度？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b673592c5dabb4c06622be0e9b25cb95ff68b41c","tid":297592,"uid":97419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"高低膊好辛苦"},{"pid":"db10665211253525516dd3d1b1460724fe7d0c02","tid":297592,"uid":113956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"做gym操胸背肌"},{"pid":"d50f635b5fc710d1b88beb0eefa0f33741ed03e6","tid":297592,"uid":10292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"我 不過唔算嚴重"},{"pid":"13b3f45a15cd70657f866d869c34d610a03a3f3d","tid":297592,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打都比喱個症困擾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n據我所知有得做手術改善但個手術會影響一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔做手術有冇其他方法可以改善?<br />\n巴打們又有冇睇過脊醫係真係醫到個病?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係痛唔係影響日常就唔好做手術喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然真係會矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申2x度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9a5b4b0f4a25cd921c553435b7b6eacd0c49f4","tid":297592,"uid":25375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"hello 戴過架一年幾留名"},{"pid":"6bbbd7b01392add70b768b156ee269cf3c3d6e87","tid":297592,"uid":10292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高低膊好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n呢個真 仲要有時俾人問做咩企到古古怪怪"},{"pid":"040f295549fb7f6841b321b893c264eac31a9297","tid":297592,"uid":90634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:30:32.000Z","msg":"條女19度留名<br />\n好想幫佢<br />\n聽講做運動會變好<br />\n<br />\n佢依家21歲"},{"pid":"2916a5a