/>"},{"pid":"3ce8dc9bb82b1b670e63cdd715215b770c8cdfe4","tid":297592,"uid":40122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"有，不過唔痛，所以冇乜點理<br />\n我尾龍骨最尾果部分舊骨入左屁股個位（仲屁股係feel到果舊硬既骨位）<br />\n如果做手術可以完全矯正番既話，應該會考慮做<br />\n<br />\nbtw追番post先我幾有興趣知多d"},{"pid":"dafb3f904ce6d1f8a44afb46d09eb7322cd223f2","tid":297592,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"10deg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c114a38faf2028ac459a658de3d15035a002b0","tid":297592,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"有冇有料脊醫推介"},{"pid":"18dbe03b4fda4f3490c7b2c124c9cdb296c2fee3","tid":297592,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:11:12.000Z","msg":"中學時check到，已經都27歲，好似20度左右。睇過脊醫唔覺有咩用，有個中醫叫用部機拉，唔覺有好到，同埋太燒錢<br />\n間唔中係有痛 唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知係咪因為咁，個人都瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891bf13bbdcb3dc10832edc84c5b3e160fb3f2db","tid":297592,"uid":46633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇有料脊醫推介</blockquote><br />\n同求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c318ffd98c6fbe64fe797086f0dc2642bb17f10","tid":297592,"uid":46633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"唔想做手術，驚有風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a4e355025a6128828a1d1ea85d6feda090ee21","tid":297592,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/011948_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F011948_d0b3244693f74